4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, requiring no prior knowledge. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, and statistics, and develop skills in creating predictive models using powerful libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. The program includes three classes a week with a maximum of 12 students per class. Participants will complete practical projects and are prepared for industry challenges. The course is available in both English and Spanish, and graduates receive a recognized certificate. More details can be found at the website: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop